{"tid":1345244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急非常重要］政府同CCTVB有意圖將琴晚元朗推比人示威者","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:05:35.000Z","uid":102476,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de0946cb1cf3c36bd4683feed2f50397fdef23e6","tid":1345244,"uid":102476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"琴晚我真係好嬲<br />\n點解香港可以搞成咁<br />\n警黑一家親<br />\n今日起身睇新聞<br />\n好多狗官都係講係示威衝突<br />\n再同同事傾計<br />\n我發現CCTVB根本就無點提過<br />\n整係睇CCTVB既同事完全唔知發生咩事<br />\nCCTVB純粹講元朗站有人聚集<br />\n依家政府同TVB根本就係想將個波推比反送中示威者<br />\n大家一定要正視呢樣野<br />\n唔可以比佢地轉移責任<br />\n指鹿為馬<br />\n香港變成咁<br />\n打到呢到<br />\n我真係有d眼濕濕"},{"pid":"c46297bb13502705d92c0e73714ad54734443f5a","tid":1345244,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef03de4eb28ef9605e57941edc3ccffb6deb4af9","tid":1345244,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"連儂牆, 落多D功夫啦"},{"pid":"e41924a7ae69adda883bb11d0d76f9adcff568b8","tid":1345244,"uid":102476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef03de4eb28ef9605e57941edc3ccffb6deb4af9","tid":1345244,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"連儂牆, 落多D功夫啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:04.000Z","msg":"連儂牆未必推到咁遠<br />\n我地仲要諗辦法推大個圈"},{"pid":"f974679429c300bd66d7b56d63eeb4882a29da77","tid":1345244,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e41924a7ae69adda883bb11d0d76f9adcff568b8","tid":1345244,"uid":102476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef03de4eb28ef9605e57941edc3ccffb6deb4af9","tid":1345244,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"連儂牆, 落多D功夫啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:04.000Z","msg":"連儂牆未必推到咁遠<br />\n我地仲要諗辦法推大個圈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"Airdrop 又好, 咩都好啦, 咩都盡做"},{"pid":"4bff4